Scenario: Perform the Count on Forward Data Item with no Forwarded Transaction in the list
Given a table entry named {FORWARD_ITEM_TABLE_EMPTY.xml} in the database
When there is a request for Forwarded Item Count given that storeid{000031}, terminalid{1234} and businessdate{20120530}
Then the Forwarded Item Count is in the following format:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="shift_jis"?><ItemForward><status>0</status><ForwardCount>0</ForwardCount></ItemForward>

